  "description": "<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 4\"><div class=\"layoutArea\"><div class=\"column\"><p><span style=\"font-family:'CIDFont+F1'\">The concept of Technology Levels has been used many times. Adapted for use in Starforged, they provide a range of tech levels centered around the level of technology that humanity achieved after reaching the Forge, as the e-drive become commonplace. It allows for some Settlements to have advanced far further – and for some to have collapsed catastrophically.</span></p></div></div></div>",
